data.description: Mid Century one story home is Located in highly sought after Ladera Heights.  This home boasts an impressive curb appeal and offers a desirable floor plan that includes formal living and dining rooms, as well as a family room.  The residence features stunning hardwood floors throughout, recessed lighting, and central heat and air for added comfort.  One of the highlights of this property is its rear yard, which is perfectly set up for entertaining.  It includes an outdoor fireplace, enclosed patio, and a spa, creating an ideal setting for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. This home wont last long.
